WEBVTT

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Shah Rukh Khan: Today
on TED Talks India,

00:00:04.200 --> 00:00:06.600
we have with us a world class musician

00:00:06.600 --> 00:00:08.430
who has an ever-changing relationship

00:00:08.430 --> 00:00:09.600
with music.

00:00:09.600 --> 00:00:12.240
From traditional musical instruments,

00:00:12.240 --> 00:00:15.080
he moved on to create music
from everyday objects

00:00:15.080 --> 00:00:18.720
and then to create rhythms 
inspired by nature.

00:00:18.720 --> 00:00:22.240
TED Talks India welcomes 
this inspired and innovative

00:00:22.240 --> 00:00:25.610
musical artist who has his own
unique relationship with music.

00:00:25.610 --> 00:00:28.570
On TED Talks India Nayi Soch 
we welcome Sivamani.

00:00:28.570 --> 00:00:32.270
(Applause and cheers)